SubjectJoint Letter from the United States of America and Canada pursuant to Paragraph 5 of the Procedures for the Implementation of Article XXI of the GENERAL AGREEMENT ON TRADE IN SERVICES (GATS).
PrecisAuthorization for the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the modifications proposed to the GATS Schedule (GATS/SC/90) of the United States of America to withdraw its Commitments on Gambling and betting services, done at Geneva on October 22, 2007.
